precis:
Authority to enter into the CANADA-ALBERTA VALUE-ADDED INDUSTRY DEVELOPMENT
PROGRAM COMPANION AGREEMENT wherein both parties agree to make financial
contributions towards research and the development of value-added products
and technologies in response to market opportunities.
